         <h2><strong>Why choose Pre-Engineered Buildings ?</strong></h2>
         <p>&nbsp;</p>
         <ul>
             <li><strong>Cost-effective</strong></li>
         </ul>
         <p>Saving material on low stress areas of the primary framing members makes <strong>Pre-Engineered Building</strong> more cost-effective than conventional <a href="http://zamilsteel.com.vn" data-aalisten="1">steel buildings</a></p>
         <ul>
             <li><strong>Quick Fabrication &amp; Installation </strong></li>
         </ul>
         <p><strong>Pre-Engineered Building systems</strong> focus on using pre-determined material stock and pre-designed connections to design and fabricate the building structures, thus significantly reducing the time required for design, fabrication and installation.</p>
         <ul>
             <li><strong>A versatile building system that fits various applications</strong></li>
         </ul>
         <p><strong>Pre-Engineered Building</strong> can be fitted with different structural accessories including mezzanine floors, crane runway beams, roof platform, catwalk and aesthetic features such as fascias, interior partitions, canopies, etc.</p>
         <p>The buildings are made fully water proof when applying our <a href="https://www.zamilsteel.com.vn/portfolio/zamil-maxseam-roof-system/" data-aalisten="1"><strong>MaxSEAM® standing seam roofing system</strong></a> with its roof drainage components and trims, making it a durable building system. The buildings can be furnished internally to serve all functions, and accessorized externally to achieve unique and aesthetically pleasing architecture designs, making it ideal for applications such as factories, warehouses, workshops, showrooms, hypermarkets, etc.</p>

